syauth (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release (Closes: #1).
    - PAM cdylib pam_syauth.so installed under
      /usr/lib/<multiarch>/security/ with mode 0644.
    - syauth CLI installed under /usr/bin/ with mode 0755 and the
      pair/list/revoke/status subcommands.
    - postinst creates /var/lib/syauth/ with mode 0700; postrm is
      deliberately silent so the bond store survives package
      operations.
    - Android companion shipped separately as a signed APK from the
      same GitHub release; see /usr/share/doc/syauth/android-setup.md.

 -- syauth contributors <noreply@anthropic.com>  Fri, 15 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
